{"tid":908380,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【第一城跌兩成】沙田第一城465萬新低價 兩房3個月劈百萬","createTime":"2018-11-19T14:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T16:27:30.000Z","uid":83582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1945ca4c8645a993eb059c2a957981482e99bf","tid":908380,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:02:21.000Z","msg":"2018年11月19日<br />\n【第一城跌兩成】沙田第一城465萬新低價 兩房3個月劈百萬 <br />\n<br />\n細價樓掀劈價潮。中原地產黎宗文表示，受市場負面消息影響，二手交投疏落。沙田第一城本月暫錄約6宗成交，市場最新錄44座中層E室易手，實用面積284方呎，兩房間隔，議價後以465萬元沽出，呎價16,373元，屬近期低價成交。<br />\n<br />\n沙田第一城同類貨高位造價近600萬元，為41座高層A室，實用面積284方呎，今年8月以598萬元成交，呎價21,056元，相隔三個月後最新成交較之低133萬元或22%，料創今年新低價。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2012年以286萬元買入單位，持貨6年，現易手賬面獲利約179萬元離場，單位升值約62.6%。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181119/58932526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181119%2F58932526&d=r7FyBJJP44Sm07i6Au9EKttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ab4dc8f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181119%2F58932526&h=af642cf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181119/58932526</a>"},{"pid":"3665df50924a0183e6a6813f0f34cbc04db7a827","tid":908380,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廢樓先會跌<br />\n<br />\n大業主3zero間乞衣劏房逆主升八成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (自稱)"},{"pid":"f4a4c0a49e7587cf47ed35530bbf7563ba7d51d3","tid":908380,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:11:47.000Z","msg":"夠喇夠喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\